s financials analysts research pulse bioan on new york stock exchange usd  aug  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description bioamber inc bioamber formerly dnp green technology inc incorporated on october   is an industrial biotechnology company which produces sustainable chemicals the companys technology platform combines industrial biotechnology and chemical catalysis to convert renewable feedstocks into sustainable chemicals that are replacements for petroleumderived chemicals which are used in a range of everyday products including plastics resins food additives and personal care products its geographical segments include europe and north america the company sells its product biosuccinic acid to customers in a range of chemical markets biosuccinic acid is a biologically produced chemically identical replacement for petroleumderived succinic acid that can be utilized to produce derivative products such as biobased  butanediol  bdo and can substitute petrochemicals such as maleic anhydride phthalic acid and adipic acid in various applications its biobased specialty chemicals can be used in multiple endmarkets and applications and serves as building blocks for a range of products used every day biosuccinic acid is used in various applications including plasticizers polyurethanes resins and coatings deicing and coolant solutions fine chemicals and lubricants as well as antifreeze solutions coolants solvents water treatment chemicals laundry tablets and bath salts artificial leather products and foams made with recycled polyethylene terephthalate petthe company is engaged in developing over three distinct technologies such as the production of succinic acid through fermentation the conversion of succinic acid into  bdo tetrahydrofuran thf and gammabutyrolactone gbl by catalyst assisted hydrogenation reaction and the production of adipic acid and other c chemical intermediates through fermentation and purification with or without catalytic conversion the company produces biosuccinic acid in a facility located in sarnia ontario which has a production capacity of over  metric tons of biosuccinic acid per year its product pipeline includes derivatives of biosuccinic acid and c building block chemicals the derivatives of biosuccinic acid include  bdo and thf and succinic acidbased polyesters the uses of  bdo are in the production of thf and polybutylene terephthalate pbt thf is used to produce spandex fibers and other performance polymers resins solvents and printing inks for plasticspbt is an engineeringgrade thermoplastic that combines mechanical and electrical properties with chemical resistance the automotive and electronics industries rely on pbt to produce connectors insulators wheel covers gearshift knobs and reinforcing beams polybutylene succinate pbs is a biodegradable polymer made by reacting succinic acid with  bdo and its applications range from single use in food service ware including cutlery cups and lids agricultural mulching film and compostable bags pbs is also used in combination with other biopolymers such as polylactic acid pla polyhydroxyalkanoate pha and poly hydroxybutyratecohydroxyvalerate phbv and with petrochemical polymers such as polypropylene polystyrene and polycarbonate the c building block chemicals include adipic acid which is primarily used in the production of nylon  fibers plastics and resins caprolactam which is an intermediate used in the production of nylon  and hexamethylenediamine hmda which is an intermediate used to produce nylon  the c building block chemicals are used in carpets engineering plastics textiles and fibers films and polyurethanes » full overview of bioan company address bioamber inc  annapolis ln n ste plymouth   mn    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation raymond land  fabrice orecchioni  mario settino  michael hartmann  james millis  » more officers  directors bioamber inc news bri