 which is located in europe and has an annual production of  tons  bioamber is a private us company with a global presence based in minnesota usa  in addition to the european plant bioamber will start building its first north american plant in sarnia ontario together with mitsui  co in   the sarnia plant will be commissioned in  with an initial capacity of  tons of biobased succinic acid which will be increased to  tons at peak production along with  tons of biobasedbdo  a second largescale commercial plant is planned with mitsui  co in map ta phut thailand as part of an agreement with pttmcc biochem  the thai plant is expected to come on stream in  and will have a capacity of  tons of biobased succinic acid and  tons of biobased bdo by   a third plant in north america or brazil is planned in partnership with mitsui  co which will bring bioamber’s combined capacity to  tonsyear for biobased succinic acid and  tonsyear for biobased bdo bioambers business model is based on open innovation and partnerships which have enabled it to be first to market with biobased succinic acid  bioamber’s partnerships extend across the value chain for renewable raw materials including mitsui  co mitsubishi chemical lanxess dupont cargill celexion and matric amongst others   view more supplier directory categories chemical additives and agents  products inhibitors and stabilizers  products molding compounds and resins  product organic chemicals  products organic solvents  product polymers and plastic resins  product resins and compounds  product thermoplastics and thermoplastic resins  product bioamber inc is also listed in these categories base and process oils food additives industrial lubricants specialty polymers and resins technical articles how the report on carcinogens uses science to meet its statutory obligations and its impact on small business jobs chemicals and raw materials bioamber speaks at the joint hearing on how the report on carcinogens uses science to meet its statut